<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">两数差乘法，计算四则混合式题时，可利用“两个数的差乘以一个数”进行运算。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">19×26-19×16=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 19×26-19×16</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=19×(26-16)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=19×10</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=190</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>